This folder contains examples for Variational Quantum Monte Carlo calculations.

Single: Simple single point VMC calculation for water 

VarMin/VMC-OPT-H2O: Variance minimization calculation for water. The input file of this example
 	can be used for most cases.
Varmin/VMC-OPT-C6H6: Variance minimization calculation for Benzene. The input file of this example
 	can be used for cases that optimization fail with jastrow_varmin_safe macro.
